FortniteMusicSparksSettings.SynchronizeMyDanceEmotesToJamTracks_Off_: <strong>Off</>: Dance emotes will play at their normal speed, and the emote music will play over the Jam Track.
FortniteMusicSparksSettings.SynchronizeMyDanceEmotesToJamTracks_On_D: <strong>On</>: Dance emotes will sync to the beat of the Jam Track, and the emote music will be muted.
FortniteMusicSparksSettings.SynchronizeMyDanceEmotesToJamTracks_Name: Synchronize My Dance Emotes to Jam Tracks
FortniteMusicSparksSettings.SynchronizeMyDanceEmotesToJamTracks_Gene: This settings changes what happens to your Dance Emotes while a Jam Track is playing.

SparksSetting.332501D14C2052DD4743AC95B5460C4C: Adjusts the volume of gameplay music in Festival.
